28 June 2017Members of the media are advised that the Minister of Communications, Ms Ayanda Dlodlo will today, 28 June 2017, delivery a keynote address at the launch of REALPOLITIK, an analysis and opinions web publication that seeks to be an alternative voice in the online media space.The event takes place as follows:Date: Wednesday, 28 June 2017 Time: 18h00 Venue: Lilliesleaf Farm, Rivonia, JHBEnquiries: Pheliswa Sebati Cell: 082 413 4609 Email: pheliswa@gcis.gov.za